t_ew&oe=66DC3E4E"}, {"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "3040197669344631", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/12386401_190339441614383_6342659427576840192_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=PctgtstfemsQ7kNvgHhkP-i&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=ArKoDP8H-5G5YAqTSiL1WZw&oh=00_AYBUUqLgBOnateRdqIBX-QMnxdoJESVX2aiiNH7V1pRUfg&oe=66DC4009"}, {"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "589231725267995", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/12331069_1692938717459161_6286521335979966464_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=2euU4n039MQQ7kNvgFwLSFU&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=ArKoDP8H-5G5YAqTSiL1WZw&oh=00_AYB-WU8KLuUKrbbOH0pIeM038LMQWRyBsxLCsBLYnVT3xQ&oe=66DC2BD1"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "YouTube VR", "keywords": ["Video", "Movies", "Shows", "TV", "Live"], "long_description": "Experience your favorite YouTube channels, videos and creators in virtual reality.\n\nThe YouTube VR app turns every video on the platform into your own virtual reality experience and reimagines YouTube as a 3D world you can explore from the inside. \n\nExperience YouTube like never before\n\u2022 Explore every video on YouTube, from 3D 360 videos to standard rectangular videos\n\u2022 Get the full, signed-in experience that lets you view subscriptions, playlists, watch history and more\n\nSee and hear it all\n\u2022 Immerse yourself in full 360-degree videos that put you at the center of the action\n\u2022 Experience spatial audio, where depth and distance play a role depending on where you look\n\u2022 Switch between voice and keyboard controls to browse and search with ease\n\n\nPermission Notice\n\u2022 Microphone: Needed to allow searching for YouTube content with your voice", "short_description": "Experience your favorite YouTube channels, videos and creators in virtual reality.\n\nThe YouTube VR app turns every video on the platform into your own virtual reality expe